msg":"多謝你哋呀 你補鐘阿sir真係好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n緊係冇阻到啦 真係救咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我考銀城 <br />\n今日唔算多車 不過都有其他突然停低阻路既車 <br />\n同埋準備轉彎去學院門口個陣 <br />\n有個姨姨推住架車仔橫過馬路 我預早停低等左一陣<br />\n後尾見學院職員出嚟拉走佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T15:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />恭喜晒，補鐘阿sir 教我禮讓，見到考試車一定要幫手，安全情況下讓車。<br />\n<br />\n早一轉去到學院門口，佢問我讓唔讓學院車出，我話讓啦，我又唔趕時間，後面又一架車都冇。睇真d 原來係考緊van.<br />\n<br />\n個師兄都呆住一陣，好似問我點解我會停低讓咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 個考官又望住我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成十秒佢先出，我等佢出晒先慢慢開返車，希望位師兄都 1 take pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T04:57:29.000Z","msg":"P牌無正皮<br />\n好有愛呀<br />\n好人有好報<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61ce6045f7de715606b30409f31961b946fcffe","tid":2471190,"uid":385415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0141846093d6232626845afcae95f5b59fb8cae","tid":2471190,"uid":195046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T02:16:34.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T04:58:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你仲乜春<br />\n過嚟搞人哋"},{"pid":"e8c3b1e13146f01f5a40160d240ca6dc43